name: Shellshore Showers
desc:
Beware traversing through the rainy terrain of Shellshore Showers with dark pitfalls and goombas hosting snappy hats! Will you prevail despite the storm?

A fairly tedious level with some backtracking required! This is actually the first level I worked on with Wildwood Ways being the second, but due to life itself I ended up finishing WW first before SS. I hope you enjoy this level!
